  "texts": [
    "Study included 130 BCa patients admitted to the Urology Department of Marmara University Pendik Training and Research Hospital between 2018 and 2020.",
    "The control group was composed of 64 volunteers who had no BCa diagnosis in their lifetime.",
    "After informed consent, the blood and urine samples were taken from BCa patients before surgery.",
    "Blood and urine samples from patients or control subjects were collected in EDTA containing tubes and sterile urine containers (first urine sample of the morning), respectively, and stored in -80 °C freezers until usage.",
    "The droplet formations were performed with or without solutions composed of salt mixtures (two mixtures, one obtained with adding 1 M KCl and the other one with 1 M KCl plus 1 M MgCl 2)."
  ],
